{"tid":1013550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實環保撚最黑人憎既地方係","createTime":"2019-02-08T12:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T12:27:39.000Z","uid":149161,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ea950c559df0957245497e64581bc07c37c8cee3","tid":1013550,"uid":149161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"係專注係芝麻綠豆嘅小事上面<br />\n例如要快餐店 kfc mcdonald 走塑<br />\n但係又無視政府，跨國企業既浪費(eg 耗用紙張)<br />\n<br />\n事實係就算市民普羅大眾肯環保<br />\n政府同跨國企業嘅浪費，唔環保都蓋過哂<br />\n更何況政府唔帶頭做推動者<br />\n又點樣令市民有環保意識呢<br />\n<br />\n所以環保撚成日jer住佢身邊既人/事物要人地環保係好撚乞人憎，因為佢哋根本放錯咗重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308b1611fdd03e83dc464e0ac8380d6f2b9eb497","tid":1013550,"uid":162380,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"因為佢地嘅目的係自我感覺良好<br />\n唔係為咗環保"},{"pid":"3b701bfb983d44bc4b58990635d3d847665bab06","tid":1013550,"uid":201482,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"因為人嘅本性就係欺善怕惡"},{"pid":"bd3b8be9280bbaacc743b0249814f54e8e7b8b57","tid":1013550,"uid":42636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:09:57.000Z","msg":"開緊冷氣回Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n吹咩"},{"pid":"58bb21ca3980eac0cb026793aea243e63885af16","tid":1013550,"uid":149161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"308b1611fdd03e83dc464e0ac8380d6f2b9eb497","tid":1013550,"uid":162380,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"因為佢地嘅目的係自我感覺良好<br />\n唔係為咗環保"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:23:38.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"9e0d9fe92837e990209c2d5a6be86262b5f2adf1","tid":1013550,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd3b8be9280bbaacc743b0249814f54e8e7b8b57","tid":1013550,"uid":42636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:09:57.000Z","msg":"開緊冷氣回Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr